se-panel rte-template js-collapse-panel-show" data-template="rte-tri-title-collapse"><div class="plate-collapse__heading"><div class="plate-collapse cke-list-block js-collapse-panel rte-template js-collapse-panel-show" data-template="rte-tri-title-collapse"><div class="plate-collapse__heading"></div></div><table style="border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%;"><tbody><tr><td style="width: 99.8647%;" colspan="2"><strong>港岛区</strong></td></tr><tr><td style="width: 28.5521%;" valign="top"><p class="p1">兴华广场</p></td><td style="width: 71.3126%;" valign="top"><p class="p1">香港柴湾环翠道 11 号兴华广场</p></td></tr></tbody></table><div class="plate-collapse cke-list-block js-collapse-panel rte-template js-collapse-panel-show" data-template="rte-tri-title-collapse"><div class="plate-collapse__heading"></div></div></div></div><div class="plate-collapse__heading"></div><div></div><div class="plate-collapse cke-list-block js-collapse-panel rte-template js-collapse-panel-show" data-template="rte-tri-title-collapse"><div class="plate-collapse__heading"><div class="plate-collapse cke-list-block js-collapse-panel rte-template js-collapse-panel-show" data-template="rte-tri-title-collapse"><div>据《信报》报道，消委会将分阶段向已登记申请退款的《选择》月刊订阅户寄送退款支票，最迟会在 3 月 31 日前收到退款支票。如订户有疑问，可致电 2856 3123 查询。</div></div></div></div><div class="plate-collapse cke-list-block js-collapse-panel rte-template js-collapse-panel-show" data-template="rte-tri-title-collapse"><div class="plate-collapse__heading"></div></div><p>消委会亦提供了教学影片，与读者分享如何使用网上版阅览《选择》月刊。消委会期望全新网上免费阅览的《选择》月刊能为市民提供权威参考，提升消费判断能力，同时协助市场维持公平竞争，并呼吁市民以可持续的方式推动消费权益。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_69547"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/bDi2ueSbKBM?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>图片来源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/photo?fbid=924537109791159&amp;set=pcb.924537163124487">选择月刊@Facebook</a></p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://www.consumer.org.hk/tc/choice-magazine/2025-free-choice">消费者委员会</a>、<a href="https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/3967774">信报</a></p><p>======</p><p>加入 <a href="https://www.threads.net/@unwirehk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">unwire thread</a> 倾倾科技背后黑暗事</p><p>========</p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/01/03/choice-magazine-free-to-watch/shop_guide/">消委会《选择》月刊网上版本月起免费看，盼助市民精明消费</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
