        <item>
            <title>掌上游戏机操控模组有得换！更多「三代」AYANEO 细节公布</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/03/more-details-announce-on-ayaneo-3-with-changable-joystick-module/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=more-details-announce-on-ayaneo-3-with-changable-joystick-module</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/03/more-details-announce-on-ayaneo-3-with-changable-joystick-module/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Edward]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 03 Jan 2025 03:00:17 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新闻]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[AYANEO]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[AYANEO 3]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1284852</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>去年不少厂商都纷纷推出自家采用 Windows 11 OS 的掌上游戏机，而且各出奇谋，竞争十分激烈，而这个新市场斗争相信去到今年将会持续。AYANEO 就率先宣布将会推出第三代的旗舰级掌上游戏机，最突破是它拥有可更换手制模组的设计，令大家可按玩哪类型的游戏而使用合适操控，相信会令打机手感直线提升。</p><p>今次发布的 AYANEO 3，设有黑、白两色设计，配置上用家可选择 AMD Ryzen 7 8840U 或 AMD Ryzen AI 9 HX 370 版本，而内建的 7 吋 1080p 荧幕，亦有支援 120Hz 更新率的 LCD 或支援 144Hz 更新率的 OLED 选择。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1284855" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ayaneo3_002-694x362.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="362" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ayaneo3_002-694x362.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ayaneo3_002.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1284856" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ayaneo3_014-694x362.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="362" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ayaneo3_014-694x362.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ayaneo3_014.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲AYANEO 3 设有黑、白两色设计。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1284857" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ayaneo3_017-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ayaneo3_017-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ayaneo3_017.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1284858" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ayaneo3_016-694x475.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="475" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ayaneo3_016-694x475.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ayaneo3_016.jpg 1276w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲配置上用家可选择 AMD Ryzen 7 8840U 或 AMD Ryzen AI 9 HX 370 版本，而内建的 7 吋 1080p 荧幕，亦有支援 120Hz 更新率的 LCD 或支援 144Hz 更新率的 OLED 选择。</p><p>不过 AYANEO 3 最突破的设计，肯定是它的一对可替换兼可自定义摆位的手制模组。有玩开掌上游戏机的用家应该都会感受到，现今市场上很难有一部掌上游戏机玩任何游戏也有一流的操控手感，而 AYANEO 3 就设有 3 对可供替换的手制模组，无论大家是想用双蘑菇 + 方向盘 + ABXY 键玩冒险游戏，还是要用到触控板玩传统策略游戏，甚或要用到 ABCXYZ 亦个动作键玩格斗类游戏（例如：拳王），它都有相对应的模组配置，基本上用家只需放入合适模组再启动游戏即可。而且不只模组可以自设，就连上下位置也可调转插入，以适应不同手形或操控习惯的用家，而调转后的按键亦可取出并以适当方向装回模组上，令调转模组插入机身时，按键上显示的文字不会上下调转，设计十分体贴。可以说的是，在设计上，AYANEO 3 配合这个全新可替换的手制模组，是现时掌上游戏机界最体贴用家操控需要的机款。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1284859" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ayaneo3_005-694x362.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="362" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ayaneo3_005-694x362.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ayaneo3_005.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲AYANEO 3 最突破的设计，肯定是这个可替换的手制模组。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1284860" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ayaneo3_010-694x363.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="363" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ayaneo3_010-694x363.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ayaneo3_010.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲它设有 3 对手制模组供用家按不同游戏选用。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1284861" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ayaneo3_011-694x364.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="364" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ayaneo3_011-694x364.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ayaneo3_011.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲模组不但可自由替换，亦可上下调转，而按键亦可取出并按合适方向装回，让不同操控习惯的用家，也可以最舒适的方式打机。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1284862" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ayaneo3_015-694x365.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="365" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ayaneo3_015-694x365.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ayaneo3_015.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲模组亦会按机身颜色而有不同设计，像白机就会配置白色手制模组。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1284863" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ayaneo3_006-694x364.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="364" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ayaneo3_006-694x364.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ayaneo3_006.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲至于接驳模组的方法，官方暂时未有透露，但笔者从影片观察估计应是采用磁吸模式，这样拆出或装上模组会是最方便。</p><p>不过现时 AYANEO 3 仍在开发阶段，所以未有更多细节公布，定价、推出日期亦有待确认。有兴趣的读者可以浏览以下官方介绍片看看 AYANEO 3 的设计有多大突破。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_13419"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/_r7L1_0C6EE?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>来源：<a href="https://www.ayaneo.com/product/AYANEO-3">AYANEO</a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/01/03/more-details-announce-on-ayaneo-3-with-changable-joystick-module/fun-tech/">掌上游戏机操控模组有得换！更多「三代」AYANEO 细节公布</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
