        <item>
            <title>日本少女再兴玩复古相机，杂讯、手震反而更有味+自创独特新影法</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/02/retrodigitalcameras-in-japan/dc/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=retrodigitalcameras-in-japan</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/02/retrodigitalcameras-in-japan/dc/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 09:12:49 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[摄影文化]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[数码相机]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[复古数码相机]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1284748</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>在智能手机影相成为主流的今天，古典轻巧数码相机再次「咸鱼翻生」，年轻一代并不一定靠手机摄影，有些人更会钟情于怀旧数码相机带来的独特摄影风格、效果，体验当时的「时代感」。日本就有电视台在街头访问年轻用户群的睇法。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1284766" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000018screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000018screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000018screenshot.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1284767" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000023screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000023screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000023screenshot.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>现代年轻朋友反而倒造怀旧摄影产品，原因是它独特的影像风格、时代感。在街头访问中，有 10 多岁、20 多岁的相机用户分享了他们对数码相机和智能手机的看法。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1284786" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000114screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000114screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000114screenshot.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1284787" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000119screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000119screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000119screenshot.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>捕捉时代感的独特选择</h2><p>一位受访者提到，使用数码相机拍摄的照片拥有特别的复古氛围。他表示：「iPhone 拍摄时，画面完全不会手震，但数码相机的微微手震反而为照片增添了特殊的质感。」另一位受访者则认为，数码相机拍出的照片色彩和颗粒感更有故事性，「它的模糊感和类似滤镜的效果让画面看起来更有趣，是一种对相片的『装扮』」。</p><p>有受访者表示她的相机来自她的母亲：「妈妈以前买的相机现在由我使用。高中时几乎所有同学都有一部，用它拍制服照特别有感觉。」</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1284769" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000157screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000157screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000157screenshot.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>回忆与新潮并存</h2><p>不少路人表示，现在使用的数码相机是从父母家中找出来的旧款型号。一位女士分享说：「我用的是妈妈以前结婚时买的数码相机，从小就看到家里有它，当时这些相机很普及，但随著智能电话拍摄画质越来越好，这些相机被冷落了。现在拿来用特别有怀旧感。」</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1284768" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/200002screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/200002screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/200002screenshot.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1284772" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000236screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000236screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000236screenshot.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>另一位受访者也提到：「朋友的家里找到了旧相机，拍摄的照片有一种穿越时光的感觉，很适合分享到社交媒体。」「相比起现在的手机，数位相机拍出的照片更像怀旧电影的画面，特别是色调和质感。」「现在我用 2006 年的数位相机拍令和时代的街景，感觉特别怀旧，甚至连快门声都让人想起过去的日子。」</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1284771" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000228screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000228screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000228screenshot.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1284773" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000242screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000242screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000242screenshot.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1284774" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000247screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000247screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000247screenshot.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>智能手机与数码相机的互补应用</h2><p>虽然这些复古数码相机有其独特魅力，受访者也提到智能手机在一些情境下仍不可或缺。一位受访者解释：「室内拍照时光线不足，我通常用手机，但在光线好的地方，例如户外，就会用复古数码相机。」另一位受访者分享了他的使用习惯：「我会用 iPhone 和数码相机交替拍摄，不同设备有不同风格。」</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1284775" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000410screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000410screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000410screenshot.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1284776" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000427screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000427screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000427screenshot.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>数码相机的时尚元素</h2><p>除了实用性，数码相机本身的外形也成为时尚标志。一位受访者提到：「持有数码相机看起来很可爱，我会在相机上挂上自制吊饰或挂件，增加个性化元素。」更有人表示，数码相机不只是一个拍摄工具，也可用来展示个人风格。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1284777" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/200056screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/200056screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/200056screenshot.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>而数码相机本身也成为一件复古潮流物品，很多人甚至希望将它入镜－－在镜子前面拍摄相片。「有些人会用镜子反射，把复古数位相机拍进相片中，让机身也成为作品的一部分。」</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1284778" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000517screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000517screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000517screenshot.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1284779" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000520screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000520screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000520screenshot.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1284780" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000330screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000330screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000330screenshot.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>现代年轻人的复古情怀</h2><p>我们能看到数码相机复兴的背后，不只是用家们对摄影器材技术的选择，同时是有一种回溯时代记忆的诉求。有受访者提到，用数码相机拍摄当下的城市风景会产生一种「时光倒流」的感觉。例如有人在使用老款相机拍摄现代的渋谷时，竟然感受到「回到平成时代」的怀旧情怀。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1284783" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000247screenshot-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000247screenshot-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000247screenshot-1.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1284781" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000317screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000317screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000317screenshot.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1284782" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/200038screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/200038screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/200038screenshot.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>复古摄影的未来</h2><p>数码相机复古热潮或许将会持续，尤其在更多人希望平衡现代科技与怀旧情怀时，数码相机的独特性成为不可替代的选择。无论是纯粹拍摄照片，还是作为展示个人品味的时尚单品，数码相机都在新世代找到自己的位置。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1284784" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000524screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000524screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000524screenshot.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1284785" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000110screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000110screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2000110screenshot.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_90365"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/DMWFp5bKdNo?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/01/02/retrodigitalcameras-in-japan/dc/">日本少女再兴玩复古相机，杂讯、手震反而更有味+自创独特新影法</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
